334	 * GGUF Quant Block Formats.
335	 * =========================================================================
336	 *
337	 * These layouts and IQ2 tables match the GGUF quantized tensor format,
338	 * reduced to only the formats ds4.c currently reads:
339	 *   - Q2_K routed down experts
340	 *   - Q4_K routed experts in the high-memory variant
341	 *   - IQ2_XXS routed gate/up experts
342	 *   - Q8_K temporary activation blocks for dot products
343	 */
